## Color Theory Workflow

- [ ] 1. Understand brand personality: What emotions should the design evoke?
- [ ] 2. Choose color harmony: Complementary, analogous, triadic, split-complementary
- [ ] 3. Apply 60-30-10 rule: Primary 60%, secondary 30%, accent 10%
- [ ] 4. Consider color psychology: What do specific colors communicate?
- [ ] 5. Ensure accessibility: Check contrast ratios for readability
- [ ] 6. Test on backgrounds: Colors must work on light and dark
- [ ] 7. Build color system: Define primary, secondary, neutrals, and usage rules

